            <div class="close-brdotml-modal modal-close">
              <i class="fas fa-xmark"></i>
            </div>

            <div class="row project">
              <div class="col-lg-6 mb-5 mb-lg-5 project-col">
                <ModalProjectPicture src={Brdotml} alt="Brdotml logo" />
                <h1><b>ðŸ‡§ðŸ‡·.ml (brdotml)</b></h1>
                <p><b>A Simple PHP URL shortener.</b></p>
                <div>
                  <a class="project-button" href="https://ðŸ‡§ðŸ‡·.ml/docs">
                    <i class="fas fa-book"></i>
                  </a>
                  <a
                    class="project-button"
                    href="https://github.com/AmanoTeam/brdotml"
                  >
                    <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
                  </a>
                  <a class="project-button" href="https://ðŸ‡§ðŸ‡·.ml">
                    <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-6 project-col project-desc">
                <p>
                  ðŸ‡§ðŸ‡·.ml is a simple URL shortener written in PHP that me
                  (Alisson) made just for learning.<br />
                  It is planned to be rewriten it in Python sometime in the future.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- customgram -->
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 sr-item text-center">
