                  <li>Max accounts increased to 10.</li>
                  <li>Option to set up a proxy before login.</li>
                  <li>Option to clear media from cache.</li>
                  <li>"Delete for everyone" enabled by default.</li>
                  <li>Upload date for profile photos.</li>
                  <li>Links and username on user bios clickable.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- DuckPy -->
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 sr-item text-center">
        <a id="duckpy-a" href="#duckpy-modal">
          <div class="service-box mt-5">
            <ProjectPicture src={Duckpy} alt="Duckpy logo" />
            <h4>Duckpy</h4>
            <p>Python module to search on DuckDuckGo.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <div id="duckpy-modal">
          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="close-duckpy-modal modal-close">
              <i class="fas fa-xmark"></i>
            </div>

            <div class="row project">
              <div class="col-lg-6 mb-5 mb-lg-5 project-col">
