                <p><b>Python module to search on DuckDuckGo.</b></p>
                <div>
                  <a
                    class="project-button"
                    href="https://github.com/AmanoTeam/duckpy"
                  >
                    <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
                  </a>
                  <a
                    class="project-button"
                    href="https://pypi.org/project/duckpy"
